All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable
Direct Known Subclasses:
PerformanceLoggingWebBroker
public class WebBroker extends MonitoringBorkerEX
A broker that takes care of the submission of web sessions to the data center it handles. The broker submits the cloudlets of the provided web sessions continuously over a specified period. Consequently clients must specify the endpoint (in terms of time) of the simulation.
Author:
nikolay.grozev

      name - - the name of the broker.
      refreshPeriod - - the period of polling web sessions for new cloudlets.
